

'''The Diamond Age. Neal Stephenson. 1995'''


Review at http://www.complete-review.com/reviews/stephenn/diamond.htm

Good entry in the Wikipedia at http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Diamond_Age


=Description=


Together with [[Snowcrash]], one of the influential SF-books of the nineties. It is particularly noted for its detailed description of a society organized in networks rather than nation-states, and for its description of different forms of collective intelligence.

